{"tid":1960640,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★再有卡拉OK出現確診 男患者唱K期間沒戴口罩 於馬莎百貨任收銀","createTime":"2020-04-06T09:26:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T09:41:30.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e6fe9e61ae8f833107968d170cd85e95701e09b5","tid":1960640,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T09:26:52.000Z","msg":"再有卡拉OK出現確診個案，男患者於皇室堡的馬莎百貨工作，主要做收銀及上貨工作。他於上月23日發病，出現流鼻水，仍有上班，期間有戴口罩及與同事午膳，他在上月25日為同事餞行，一行7人到銅鑼灣CEO Neway卡拉OK消遣，唱K期間沒有戴口罩。而唱K的同事中亦有1宗初步確診個案。該名男患者的妻子早前確診，根據發病日期，疑被男患者傳染。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200406/bkn-20200406123434058-0406_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200406%2Fbkn-20200406123434058-0406_00822_001.html&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLR1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=9955c35c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200406/bkn-20200406123434058-0406_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f1db9c46b26b3606529892d05f7b1fe0e1cee145","tid":1960640,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T09:27:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18f48d391828558833141b78793c8796d3096361","tid":1960640,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T09:28:00.000Z","msg":"Neway顧客馮小姐：不會戴口罩「唱K」，自己有做運動，不擔心受感染<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1952323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https: